      "content": "look i dont need a \"financial advisor\" i need to stay off the radar of people who know how to bypass standard banking protocols. if you wont help with the scrub, at least tell me if u think the pattern i'm seeing—the micro-transfers out of the old accounts—is typical for a surveillance operation or if i'm just being paranoid. it feels too specific to be a coincidence.",
